headline: 3 Growth Companies With High Insider Ownership And Up To 37% Revenue Growth
summary: The market has climbed by 2.0% over the past week, with every sector up, contributing to a 12% increase over the last 12 months. In this context of overall growth and an optimistic forecast for earnings to grow by 14% annually, companies that exhibit both substantial revenue growth and high insider ownership can be particularly appealing for investors seeking alignment between management interests and shareholder value.
